data.description: Stunning new construction home ready for move-in! This Craftsman style colonial boasts over 4,000 square feet of elegant living. Finishes are top notch. Thoughtful upgrades everywhere. Upgraded lighting & custom closets throughout. Storage for days in this gorgeous kitchen with expansive island. Sun streams through the wall of windows w/ a slider to the patio. Entertainer’s dream w/ the kitchen open to the family room. Dedicated mudroom organizes the chaos w/ built-in cubbies, bench and dream walk-in pantry. First floor bedroom w/ amazing full bath & walk-in closet w/ built-ins. Wide staircase leads to second level w/ 3 additional bedrooms, home office, laundry room & dedicated storage room. Primary suite has massive walk-in closet & en-suite bathroom streaming w/ sunshine & a soaking tub. Finished basement w/ huge tv/play room, exercise room & a full bath. Walk to elementary school & courts & fields across the street. Acton/Boxborough school system is the icing on the cake!
